<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,361,1743,1769]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Distribution:</emphasis>
<collectingCountry box="[368,431,1744,1770]" name="India" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">India</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[443,559,1744,1770]" name="Myanmar" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1436,325,1807]" box="[198,785,1781,1807]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,462,1781,1807]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Seasonal occurrence:</emphasis>
Collected in June and July.
</paragraph>
